Package org.cripac.isee.vpe.data

This package contains classes for data managing.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataManagingApp

    GraphDatabaseConnector
    The class GraphDatabaseConnector is the base class for connector to graph databases.
    GraphDatabaseConnector.Link
    The class Link represents a link from one node to another in the graph database.
    HDFSReader
    The HDFSReader class is the base class for classes that read and parse data from HDFS.
    WebCameraConnector
    The WebCameraConnector is the base class for all web camera connector classes.
